		<h2>Food <span class="small">for the</span> Soul</h2>
<h4>Community Service</h4>
<p>We believe that this world and the communities where we live, are only as good as what we’re willing to give back. Allebach Communications has been acting upon this belief from the start of the company.</p>
<p>We are very active in supporting and serving in local charities as well as global humanitarian efforts. Here are a few examples of the groups that we have and are supporting:</p>
<ul>
<li>Give Hope to Honduras–Central America</li>
<li>Shores of Grace–Brazil</li>
<li>Boys &amp; Girls Club of America</li>
<li>Keystone Opportunity Center</li>
<li>Penn Foundation -- Mental Health Foundation serving NE Pennsylvania</li>
<li>North Penn United Way</li>
<li>Youth Career Development–working with local schools on career pathways for students</li>
<li>Morning Star–Maternity Home</li>
<li>Community Arts</li>
</ul>
